short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: The supplementary extension for the MyASUS for Chromebook PWA.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
You should use this extension with MyASUS for Chromebook, so the System Info & Diag function will be supported on MyASUS for Chromebook. If you want to confirm the list of supported models, please refer to the following website.
Support model list: https://www.asus.com/support/faq/1050020/#C32

MyASUS for Chromebook(PWA): https://dlcdnccls.asus.com/app/myasus_for_chromebook
